<plot>Famed American writer Ambrose Bierce disappeared in Mexico during the revolution of 1913-1914 and was never heard from again. This short film interweaves a thread from Bierce's most famous story, "An Occurrence at Owl Creek Bridge" with speculation as to a possible scenario for Bierce's fate.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?026369</url></doc>
